---
import "../styles/global.css";
import Carousel from "../components/Carousel.astro";
import SimpleSlider from "../components/SimpleSlider.astro";
---

<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
		<title>Jesus's Portfolio</title>
	</head>
	<body>
		<header class="header-element-first">
			<h1 class="flex flex-col items-start w-[60vw]">
				<strong class="text-2xl">Hello! I'm Jesus</strong><br /><span
					class="rainbow-text">Fullstack Developer</span
				>
			</h1>
			<p class="text-start w-[80vw]">
				<strong>+1 year experience.</strong> Web and Desktop App Developer.
				Specialized in building end-to-end Applications.
			</p>
			<nav class="flex w-full px-[10vw] font-bold text-shadow-xs text-shadow-black">
				<a class="flex justify-center w-1/3 bg-blue-500 rounded-l-md hover:bg-pink-500" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/jesus-mendoza-736a74282/">Linkedin</a>
				<a class="flex justify-center w-1/3 bg-sky-500 hover:bg-pink-500" href="https://github.com/JesusMG24">GitHub</a>
				<a class="flex justify-center w-1/3 bg-zinc-500 rounded-r-md hover:bg-pink-500" href="mailto:albertomendozax9800@gmail.com">e-mail</a>
			</nav>
		</header>
		<section class="section-element-first">
			<h2 class="h2-element-first">
				<strong>Experience & Knowledge</strong>
			</h2>
			<Carousel>
				<li class="li-element-first">
					<h3 class="h3-element-first">Independent Developer</h3>
					<p class="p-element-second">Aug 2024 - Present</p>
					<p class="p-element-first">
						Built multiple Fullstack Apps, always focusing in
						Responsive Mobile First Designs, API Efficiency and
						Database Query Optimization.
					</p>
				</li>
				<li class="li-element-first">
					<h3 class="h3-element-first">
						Self-taught Frontend Journey
					</h3>
					<p class="p-element-second">Jan 2024 - July 2024</p>
					<p class="p-element-first">
						Deep Dived into Frontend Development from CSS libraries
						like Bootstrap or Tailwind to the complex corners of
						React and its frameworks such as Next.js or Redux.
					</p>
				</li>
				<li class="li-element-first">
					<h3 class="h3-element-first">College Taught Knowledge</h3>
					<p class="p-element-second">Aug 2020 - Dec 2022</p>
					<p class="p-element-first">
						During my classes in Software Engineering I concealed my
						first introduction to programming languages like Python,
						PHP and C#, learning through the development of
						Fullstack CRUD Apps, Data Structure Implementations,
						Simple Automation Scripts, etc.
					</p>
				</li>
				<li class="li-element-first">
					<h3 class="h3-element-first">Game Developer Enthusiast</h3>
					<p class="p-element-second">2018 - 2020</p>
					<p class="p-element-first">
						Next to a friend we started a journey in which we
						dreamed of developing a videogame, although those tries
						were unsuccessful, I was able to drive myself through
						Unreal Engine learning and developing in the beautiful
						C++ language.
					</p>
				</li>
				<li class="li-element-first">
					<h3 class="h3-element-first">JavaScript Obsession</h3>
					<p class="p-element-second">Aug 2014 - 2018</p>
					<p class="p-element-first">
						The years to come are bloated with JavaScript
						experimenting, being the videogame Minecraft the epitome
						of such efforts, while the game itself is written in
						Java, most of its mod's config files were in JavaScript.
					</p>
				</li>
				<li class="li-element-first">
					<h3 class="h3-element-first">
						Web Development Summer Course
					</h3>
					<p class="p-element-second">May 2014 - Aug 2014</p>
					<p class="p-element-first">
						My first approach to the principles of Web Development
						and Programming Languages, building dozens of landing
						pages with the recently acquired skills in HTML, CSS and
						JavaScript.
					</p>
				</li>
			</Carousel>
